headline: Is It Too Late To Consider TransDigm Group (TDG) After Strong Multi‑Year Share Price Gains?
summary: If you are wondering whether TransDigm Group's current share price still makes sense, you are in the right place. This article focuses squarely on what you are paying versus what you may be getting. The stock most recently closed at US$1,448.55, with returns of 4.8% over 7 days, 13.4% over 30 days, 6.6% year to date, 14.0% over 1 year, 144.1% over 3 years and 220.2% over 5 years.
